Citifit
=======
A Google App Engine service linking Citibike accounts with Fitbit accounts.

Citifit is a simple service running on top of Google App Engine that makes it
possible to automatically log Citibike activity to a Fitbit account.

Setup
=====
First, install the required packages.

  cd citifit
  virtualenv -p /usr/bin/python2.7 --no-site-packages --distribute .

  ./bin/pip2.7 install fitbit
  ./bin/pip2.7 install pytz
  ./bin/pip2.7 install enum34
  ./bin/pip2.7 install google-api-python-client

Second, update the application field in the app.yaml with your Google App Engine
application name.

Third, add your keys for the different services to conf.py.
